data.description: Discover paradise in this stunning 3-bedroom, 3-bathroom Florida Keys home nestled along the serene boating canals of Saddlebunch Key. Only a 10-15 minute boat ride from your dock to open ocean! Enjoy the privacy of a lush fenced in, tropical landscaped yard, take a nap in a hammock under the banana trees, relax in the sun kissed living room, and savor culinary delights in the updated kitchen. Double balconies await you for coffee in the mornings overlooking the sunrise, while peekaboo ocean views from the front bedroom greet you for the Florida Key's famous sunsets every evening.Playgrounds, tennis & volleyball courts are a short bike ride away at the neighborhood entrance and sit just behind a local treasure, Baby's coffee. Just a short 14 mile drive from Key West's vibrant hotspots, this home offers the perfect blend of tranquility and accessibility. Embrace the Florida Keys lifestyle with this tropical oasis.**Low insurances are the cherry on top with current homeowners combined with hurricane at $3,470.94 and flood at $625!**
